gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 108, Thunder 105
gameRecap.excerpt: Despite Donovan Mitchells 43 points (15-27 FG), 8 rebounds, and five assists, the Cavaliers fall to the Thunder, 108-105. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander led the way for the Thunder with 34 points, 11 rebounds, four assists, and five steals, while Chet Holmgren added 16 points, 13 rebounds, and seven blocks in the victory. Evan Mobley tallied 14 points, 15 rebounds, and three assists for the Cavaliers in the losing effort. The Thunder improve to 2-0, while the Cavaliers fall to 1-1.
